        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cover a<strong> tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>(to prevent the fish from sticking!)</p><p>Add the <strong>coated hake</strong> to the baking tray[s] and place under the grill for 6-7 min or until the fish is cooked through and starting to char – this is your <strong>tandoori hake</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
